nodes.text: A Poletec test subject was a Poletec captured by the Techno Union to be used as a test subject. Foreman of the Techno Union, Wat Tambor, had the Decimator tested on this Poletec, vaporizing him.
This Poletec did not make an appearance in the revival of The Clone Wars TV series, as in the finished version of "On the Wings of Keeradaks," the Decimator is not tested on anyone.
